# [CDNI](../wg/cdni.html)

## Summary

The CDNI Working Group met at IETF 126. The session focused on reviewing active milestones, reconciling error reporting models in the Control/Triggers interface, simplifying protected secrets metadata, progressing the Metadata Expression Language (MEL) grammar and semantics based on initial implementation feedback, and discussing logging extensions. The group also planned for a virtual interim meeting in September.

